WEBVTT

00:16.440 --> 00:24.560
21. And I saw a new heaven and a new earth, for the first heaven and the first earth were

00:24.560 --> 00:35.460
and there was no more sea. And I, John, saw the holy city, new Jerusalem, coming down

00:35.460 --> 00:41.660
from God out of heaven, prepared as a bride adorned for her husband. And I heard a great

00:41.660 --> 00:50.680
voice out of heaven saying, Behold, the tabernacle of God is with men, and he will dwell with

00:50.680 --> 00:57.440
them, and they shall be his people, and God himself shall be with them and be their God.

00:57.740 --> 01:04.240
And God shall wipe away all tears from their eyes, and there shall be no more death, neither

01:04.240 --> 01:11.460
sorrow nor crying, neither shall there be any more pain, for the former things are passed

01:11.460 --> 01:21.920
away. And he that sat upon the throne said, Behold, I make all things new. And he said

01:21.920 --> 01:33.260
unto me, Write, for these words are true and faithful. And he said unto me, It is done.

01:34.080 --> 01:41.280
I am Alpha and Omega, the beginning and the end. I will give unto him that is a thirst

01:41.280 --> 01:47.980
of the fountain of the water of life freely. He that overcometh shall inherit all things,

01:48.400 --> 01:56.460
and I will be his God, and he shall be my son. But the fearful and unbelieving and the

01:56.460 --> 02:03.420
abominable and murderers and whoremongers and sorcerers and idolaters and all liars

02:03.420 --> 02:09.240
shall have their part in the lake which burneth with fire and brimstone, which is the second

02:09.240 --> 02:15.940
death. And there came unto me one of the seven angels which had the seven vials full

02:15.940 --> 02:23.720
of the seven last plagues, and talked with me, saying, Come hither, I will shew thee

02:23.720 --> 02:30.860
the bride, the Lamb's wife. And he carried me away in the spirit to a great and high

02:30.860 --> 02:37.520
mountain and shewed me that great city, the holy Jerusalem, descending out of heaven from

02:37.520 --> 02:44.960
God, having the glory of God. And her light was like unto a stone most precious, even

02:44.960 --> 02:52.360
like a jasper stone, clear as crystal, and had a wall great and high, and had twelve

02:52.360 --> 02:58.500
gates, and at the gates twelve angels, and names written thereon which are the names

02:58.500 --> 03:05.860
of the twelve tribes of the children of Israel. On the east three gates, on the north three

03:05.860 --> 03:12.900
gates, on the south three gates, and on the west three gates. And the wall of the city

03:12.900 --> 03:20.340
had twelve foundations, and in them the names of the twelve apostles of the Lamb. And he

03:20.340 --> 03:25.820
that talked with me had a golden reed to measure the city and the gates thereof and the wall

03:25.820 --> 03:32.680
thereof. And the city lieth foursquare, and the length is as large as the breadth, and

03:32.680 --> 03:38.980
he measured the city with the reed, twelve thousand furlongs. The length and the breadth

03:38.980 --> 03:45.040
and the height of it are equal. And he measured the wall thereof, and hundred and forty and

03:45.040 --> 03:51.020
four cubits according to the measure of a man, that is, of the angel. And the building

03:51.020 --> 03:58.260
of the wall of it was of jasper, and the city was pure gold, like unto clear glass. And

03:58.260 --> 04:03.840
the foundations of the wall of the city were garnished with all manner of precious stones.

04:04.360 --> 04:11.860
The first foundation was jasper, the second sapphire, the third a chalcedony, the fourth

04:12.080 --> 04:20.260
an emerald, the fifth sardonyx, the sixth sardius, the seventh chrysolite, the eighth

04:20.260 --> 04:28.240
beryl, the ninth a topaz, the tenth a chrysoprasis, the eleventh a jasonth, the twelfth a chrysolite,

04:28.260 --> 04:36.500
an amethyst. And the twelve gates were twelve pearls. Every several gate was of one pearl,

04:36.860 --> 04:44.200
and the street of the city was pure gold, as it were transparent glass. And I saw no

04:44.200 --> 04:49.760
temple therein, for the Lord God Almighty and the Lamb are the temple of it. And the

04:49.760 --> 04:55.280
city had no need of the sun, neither of the moon, to shine in it, for the glory of God

04:55.280 --> 05:01.380
did lighten it, and the Lamb is the light thereof. And the nations of them which are

05:01.380 --> 05:06.440
saved shall walk in the light of it, and the kings of the earth do bring their glory and

05:06.440 --> 05:12.580
honor into it. And the gates of it shall not be shut at all by day, for there shall be

05:12.580 --> 05:19.240
no night there. And they shall bring the glory and honor of the nations into it, and there

05:19.240 --> 05:25.360
shall in no wise enter into it anything that defileth, neither whatsoever worketh abomination

05:25.360 --> 05:31.480
or maketh a lie, but they which are written in the Lamb's Book of Life.

